{"tid":2140156,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"【中美角力】混淆導彈和核彈 胡錫進疑遭解放軍暗批","createTime":"2020-08-04T20:18:07.000Z","updateTime":"2020-08-05T01:06:50.000Z","uid":321002,"like":1,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":2,"replies":[{"pid":"2e6546233af592401a237ab431822d3487555999","tid":2140156,"uid":321002,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-04T20:18:07.000Z","msg":"【中美角力】混淆導彈和核彈 胡錫進疑遭解放軍暗批<br />\n中美對峙升級，《環球時報》總編輯胡錫進主張，中國核武庫大幅擴容對抗美國，但胡錫進言論懷疑引起解放軍不滿。有解放軍退役軍官不點名批評，有人「惡意炒作」中國核武問題，涉嫌指責軍隊不作為，並為敵對國家攻擊中國提供話柄。事實上，胡錫進所言也顯示，他似乎混淆了核彈和導彈兩個概念，惹來批評並不難理解。<br />\n<br />\n胡錫進近月在微博提出，中國需要「在較短時間內，將核彈頭數量擴大到千枚水平，包括至少有100枚東風-41戰略導彈」，以抑制美國的戰略野心和對華衝動。胡錫進此言引起多方關注和熱議。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://china.hket.com/article/2714615/%E3%80%90%E4%B8%AD%E7%BE%8E%E8%A7%92%E5%8A%9B%E3%80%91%E6%B7%B7%E6%B7%86%E5%B0%8E%E5%BD%88%E5%92%8C%E6%A0%B8%E5%BD%88%20%E8%83%A1%E9%8C%AB%E9%80%B2%E7%96%91%E9%81%AD%E8%A7%A3%E6%94%BE%E8%BB%8D%E6%9A%97%E6%89%B9\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fchina.hket.com%2Farticle%2F2714615%2F%25E3%2580%2590%25E4%25B8%25AD%25E7%25BE%258E%25E8%25A7%2592%25E5%258A%259B%25E3%2580%2591%25E6%25B7%25B7%25E6%25B7%2586%25E5%25B0%258E%25E5%25BD%2588%25E5%2592%258C%25E6%25A0%25B8%25E5%25BD%2588%2520%25E8%2583%25A1%25E9%258C%25AB%25E9%2580%25B2%25E7%2596%2591%25E9%2581%25AD%25E8%25A7%25A3%25E6%2594%25BE%25E8%25BB%258D%25E6%259A%2597%25E6%2589%25B9&d=Iz1eZ%2FSDqTYQUikxH7ZeajeipyOQHODmSSmjwmLFmyk%3D&h=f81c1134\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://china.hket.com/article/2714615/%E3%80%90%E4%B8%AD%E7%BE%8E%E8%A7%92%E5%8A%9B%E3%80%91%E6%B7%B7%E6%B7%86%E5%B0%8E%E5%BD%88%E5%92%8C%E6%A0%B8%E5%BD%88%20%E8%83%A1%E9%8C%AB%E9%80%B2%E7%96%91%E9%81%AD%E8%A7%A3%E6%94%BE%E8%BB%8D%E6%9A%97%E6%89%B9</a><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/ass